
"smart_sources:Research/@kou_cyathane_2019.md": {"path":"Research/@kou_cyathane_2019.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"19qth59","at":1774951884833},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1774951829641,"size":3101,"at":1774951884833,"hash":"19qth59"},"blocks":{"#---frontmatter---":[1,101],"#Cyathane diterpenoids and drimane sesquiterpenoids with neurotrophic activity from cultures of the fungus Cyathus africanus.":[103,107],"#Cyathane diterpenoids and drimane sesquiterpenoids with neurotrophic activity from cultures of the fungus Cyathus africanus.#{1}":[105,107]},"outlinks":[{"title":"Author/Rong-Wei Kou","target":"Author/Rong-Wei Kou","line":78},{"title":"Author/Rong-Wei Kou","target":"Author/Rong-Wei Kou","line":79},{"title":"Author/Shizheng Du","target":"Author/Shizheng Du","line":80},{"title":"Author/Shuang-Tian Du","target":"Author/Shuang-Tian Du","line":81},{"title":"Author/Yixiao Li","target":"Author/Yixiao Li","line":82},{"title":"Author/Yi-Xiao Li","target":"Author/Yi-Xiao Li","line":83},{"title":"Author/Xi-Tao Yan","target":"Author/Xi-Tao Yan","line":84},{"title":"Author/Xiaohai Yan","target":"Author/Xiaohai Yan","line":85},{"title":"Author/Xi-Tao Yan","target":"Author/Xi-Tao Yan","line":86},{"title":"Author/Qiang Zhang","target":"Author/Qiang Zhang","line":87},{"title":"Author/Qiang Zhang","target":"Author/Qiang Zhang","line":88},{"title":"Author/Qiang Zhang","target":"Author/Qiang Zhang","line":89},{"title":"Author/Qiang Zhang","target":"Author/Qiang Zhang","line":90},{"title":"Author/Chenyu Cao","target":"Author/Chenyu Cao","line":91},{"title":"Author/Chen-Yu Cao","target":"Author/Chen-Yu Cao","line":92},{"title":"Author/Xia Yin","target":"Author/Xia Yin","line":93},{"title":"Author/Xia Yin","target":"Author/Xia Yin","line":94},{"title":"Author/Jin-Ming Gao","target":"Author/Jin-Ming Gao","line":95},{"title":"Author/Jin-Ming Gao","target":"Author/Jin-Ming Gao","line":96},{"title":"PDF","target":"biblib/kou_cyathane_2019/kou_cyathane_2019.pdf","line":98}],"metadata":{"id":"kou_cyathane_2019","type":"article-journal","title":"Cyathane diterpenoids and drimane sesquiterpenoids with neurotrophic activity from cultures of the fungus Cyathus africanus.","issued":{"date-parts":[[2019]]},"DOI":"10.1038/s41429-018-0106-3","container-title":"The Journal of Antibiotics","abstract":"Five terpenoids, including two new cyathane diterpenoids neocyathin S (1) and neocyathin T (2), together with three drimane sesquiterpenoids, one known 3β,6β-dihydroxycinnamolide (3), two new ones 3β,6α-dihydroxycinnamolide (4) and 2-keto-3β,6β-dihydroxycinnamolide (5), were isolated from the cultures of the basidiomycete Cyathus africanus. Their structures were established based on extensive spectroscopic methods including 2D NMR (HSQC, 1H‒1H-COSY, HMBC, ROESY) and HRESIMS experiments. The absolute configurations of two pairs of epimers, 1 and 2 as well as 3 and 4, were determined by ECD quantum chemical calculation. All the five compounds enhanced nerve growth factor (NGF)-mediated neurite outgrowth using rat pheochromocytoma (PC12) cells at concentration 10µM.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Kou","given":"Rong-Wei","literal":""},{"family":"Kou","given":"Rong-Wei","literal":""},{"family":"Du","given":"Shizheng","literal":""},{"family":"Du","given":"Shuang-Tian","literal":""},{"family":"Li","given":"Yixiao","literal":""},{"family":"Li","given":"Yi-Xiao","literal":""},{"family":"Yan","given":"Xi-Tao","literal":""},{"family":"Yan","given":"Xiaohai","literal":""},{"family":"Yan","given":"Xi-Tao","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Qiang","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Qiang","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Qiang","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Qiang","literal":""},{"family":"Cao","given":"Chenyu","literal":""},{"family":"Cao","given":"Chen-Yu","literal":""},{"family":"Yin","given":"Xia","literal":""},{"family":"Yin","given":"Xia","literal":""},{"family"